---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy & Legal Disclaimers | Mark The Bagger"
  description="Privacy policy, affiliate disclaimer, cookie preferences, and CCPA Do Not Sell opt-out for howtokillgophers.com."
>
  <header>
    <h1>Privacy & Disclaimers</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">The boring but necessary legal stuff.</p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Amazon Affiliate Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases. This means if you click on an affiliate link and buy a trap or gasser, I may receive a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps fund the hosting for this site and keeps the hardware running.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>Privacy & Cookies</h2>
      <p>This site uses a third-party open-source consent platform to manage cookie preferences. Third-party vendors, including Google, may use cookies to measure usage and improve advertising relevance.</p>
      <p>You can update your consent choices at any time using the cookie preferences panel.</p>
      <p><button type="button" class="btn" onclick="window.CookieConsent?.showPreferences()">Open Cookie Preferences</button></p>
    </section>

    <section id="do-not-sell" class="card">
      <h2>Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information</h2>
      <p>This site does not sell or share personal information with third parties for advertising purposes. The only data collected is email addresses submitted voluntarily through the signup form, used solely to send gopher control tips from Mark. To be removed from the email list, reply to any email or contact <strong>hello@howtokillgophers.com</strong>.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>General Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The methods described on this site are for informational purposes. Always check your local and state wildlife laws regarding pest control, trapping, and the use of chemical deterrents before taking action. Stay safe and read the manuals on your gear.</p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>